&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Team:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re simplifying the chaos of the events industry through powerful, easy-to-use technology. We&#39;re a self-proclaimed mix of &quot;events nerds&quot; and &quot;technology nerds&quot;, but mostly we&#39;re all passionate problem solvers who are dedicated to empowering our users. We’ve been voted DC’s Best Startup the past 2 years in a row and were called one of “DC’s Coolest Places to Work” in 2020. We’re at an exciting time in our company’s growth, and are looking for our next rockstar teammate….could that be you?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
