&lt;li&gt;Maximizing existing sales pipeline by maturing cold opportunities and qualifying inbound leads&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Scheduling demos for Sales Executives through warm and cold calling and diligent follow-up&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintaining accurate and timely records of accounts within CRM database, including pipeline reporting, new customer data, and existing client data to surface business opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Acting as day-to-day support to the entire Sales team to reach both personal and team goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
