&lt;li&gt;Ability to learn new technology quickly and thoroughly, including the&amp;nbsp;use of AI beyond the basics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional people skills (with a wide variety of personalities)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional listening skills (with an understanding of consultative sales techniques)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Outstanding verbal and written communication skills (superior grammar and spelling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;required)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A knack for persuasion and/or reframing situations with positivity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated solution-oriented mindset, organizational skills, attention to detail, and disciplined execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strong Preference for Applicants with any of the following experience:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SaaS sales experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Events industry experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Or experience with any of the following tools: Hubspot, Intercom, JIRA, Excel, Google&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sheets, Zoom&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
