&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Company&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Goodshuffle Pro is business operations &amp;amp; e-commerce software for the events industry. It manages our vendors&#39; quotes, contracts, sales pipeline, customer communications, inventory management, reporting and more. Our vendors and their staff live and breathe within this application to make their entire business run.&lt;/p&gt;
